OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start to the day with
OL,6,Fsome hazy sunshine. Showers then
OL,7,Fdeveloping in the afternoon but most
OL,8,Fplaces remaining dry with sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Still warm for the time of
OL,10,Fyear although temperatures
OL,11,Fsignificantly down compared to
OL,12,Fprevious days.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FAny showers should quickly
OL,15,Fdissipate. A dry and clear night to
OL,16,Ffollow with the wind easing light.
OL,17,FRemaining mild in urban areas but much
OL,18,Fcooler in rural spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
