OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA dry morning with hazy
OL,6,Fsunshine. The cloud thickens
OL,7,Fthroughout the day with areas seeing
OL,8,Fsome rain by the afternoon. Rain
OL,9,Fbecoming widespread and heavier by the
OL,10,Fevening and overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,13,Fgrey and wet start for some on Tuesday
OL,14,Fwith showers to follow. Settled start
OL,15,Fto Wednesday but turning wet and windy
OL,16,Flater on with further blustery showers
OL,17,Fon Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
